{"tid":750963,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"叫三次落樓一齊食飯都唔去，最後條女畀人撬走，是否抵死","createTime":"2018-07-21T12:08:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-21T13:01:00.000Z","uid":78253,"like":34,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"989c11e6fe183a96492267ec4786fefbc58f12bf","tid":750963,"uid":78253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T12:08:40.000Z","msg":"一齊10年<br />\n喺男朋友屋企樓下同個見過兩次面嘅異性第一次食飯<br />\n條女期間msg加埋打電話叫咗三次住樓上條仔落嚟陪佢<br />\n以食咗飯再食會肥唔落嚟<br />\n最後條女仲打包埋俾個男朋友<br />\n之後條女就畀呢個先識咗無耐嘅狗公撬走，呢條仔是否抵死？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 抵撚死，自動通報想你緊吓都唔理人，平時好極有限<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 條女係雞係公廁"},{"pid":"0205993c9c2bde0826f437aae1155324f54ab2f6","tid":750963,"uid":7996,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T12:14:12.000Z","msg":"一齊左十年都咁容易就分開"},{"pid":"19a0c65222e53b3a9c32b86201cca68d0b981c5d","tid":750963,"uid":63588,"like":17,"dislike":2,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T12:15:30.000Z","msg":"1999"},{"pid":"ad4828423b1eb799f0f89d7c558caa8145fe94d9","tid":750963,"uid":2572,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T12:16:04.000Z","msg":"條仔仆街唔代表你唔係雞"},{"pid":"19203d9c16a56bd41f32c11d8e5bfc12e5d89b1e","tid":750963,"uid":6532,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T12:20:22.000Z","msg":"點解我第一句已經睇唔明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0003eff83f3e75bfac0ff601fc2fd8ce1efcdd30","tid":750963,"uid":1082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T12:21:25.000Z","msg":"可惜正負皮無得㩒晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e964ae807429c392cd75e60a8d6efae936caa5a3","tid":750963,"uid":146299,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T12:25:07.